did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle:
Veterinary Reprint and Pamphlet Collection,
1865-1950
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Veterinary reprints and pamphlets dating from 1865-1950. Many authored by faculty of the New York state College of Veterinary Medicine at Cornell University.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Veterinary reprints and pamphlets dating from 1865-1950. Many authored by faculty of the New York State College of Veterinary Medicine at Cornell University.

controlaccess.head: Names:
controlaccess.persname: New York State College of Veterinary Medicine--Faculty.

prefercite.head: Cite As:
prefercite.p: Veterinary Reprint and Pamphlet Collection, #24-04-3369. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.

acqinfo.head: PROVENANCE
acqinfo.p: Most of the collection was transferred from the Flower-Sprecher Veterinary Library.Additional reprints were separated from the Veranus Moore papers and the Myron Fincher papers.

arrangement.head: COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by author. Government publications without an explicit author are filed at the end.
